How to run

From the root of the project, execute each exercise using:

python3 ex00/ft_command_quest.py [arguments]
python3 ex01/ft_score_analytics.py [scores]


Examples:

python3 ex00/ft_command_quest.py hello world
python3 ex01/ft_score_analytics.py 1500 2300 1800 2100 1950

Notes

All programs use only the Python standard library.

The output format strictly follows the subject requirements.

No external dependencies are required.

